OL,3,CUK parents put off having more kids by
OL,4,CEurope's worst paternity leave
OL,6,FThe UK has the worst statutory
OL,7,Fpaternity leave in Europe, and it's
OL,8,Fputting parents off having more
OL,9,Fchildren, a survey shared with ITV
OL,10,FNews has found.
OL,12,FBritish fathers are entitled to just
OL,13,Ftwo weeks off work after their child
OL,14,Fis born and are paid a maximum of
OL,15,F#187.18 a week - less than minimum
OL,16,Fwage.
OL,18,FIt's the least generous scheme in
OL,19,FEurope, according to the Joseph
OL,20,FRowntree Foundation, and one of the
OL,21,Fworst of the world's richest countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
