OL,6,FIn Spain, dads get 16 weeks off work
OL,7,Fon full pay, while in Sweden, they get
OL,8,F34 weeks off on up to 80% of their
OL,9,Fnormal salary.
OL,11,FCampaigners say the family can benefit
OL,12,Fhugely from staying together for
OL,13,Flonger during those early weeks.
OL,14,FFathers can spend more time bonding
OL,15,Fwith the baby and supporting the
OL,16,Fmother after the life-changing,
OL,17,Fsometimes traumatic experience of
OL,18,Fchildbirth.
