OL,6,FMother Kerry Whiteway told ITV News
OL,7,Fhow she was diagnosed with PTSD and
OL,8,Fpostnatal depression after giving
OL,9,Fbirth to her daughter.
OL,11,F"Things went from a very calm and
OL,12,Fhappy moment of new parents holding
OL,13,Four newborn baby to there being an
OL,14,Fissue, and suddenly I'm having to be
OL,15,Fwhisked off into theatre, taken away
OL,16,Ffrom my husband and my newborn child.
