OL,6,F"When we returned home, I wasn't
OL,7,Ffeeling like I should do as a new mum,
OL,8,Fand they diagnosed me with postnatal
OL,9,Fdepression. The thing I needed and
OL,10,Fwanted most in that time was my
OL,11,Fhusband."
OL,13,FHer partner, Dan, used his two weeks'
OL,14,Fstatutory paternity pay and an
OL,15,Fadditional two weeks of annual leave
OL,16,Fto support her, but after those four
OL,17,Fweeks was forced to return to work.
