OL,6,FThe Dad Shift - which organised what
OL,7,Fit described as the "world's first
OL,8,Fdads strike" this summer - says
OL,9,Fimproving the UK's paternity leave
OL,10,Fcould be an easy way to encourage
OL,11,Fbigger families.
OL,13,FProtesting dads attended what they
OL,14,Fdescribed as the 'world's first dad
OL,15,Fstrike' this summer
OL,17,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,18,Fhas expressed her worries about the
OL,19,FUK's falling birth rate.
