OL,6,FMs Phillipson said people were scared
OL,7,Foff having children due to the high
OL,8,Fcosts, and wanted "more young people
OL,9,Fto have children, if they so choose".
OL,11,FIt's a problem affecting mostly lower-
OL,12,Fincome families. High earners are more
OL,13,Flikely to be able to afford a
OL,14,Ftemporary pay cut or work for one of
OL,15,Fthe few companies that offer enhanced
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,FIn 2015, a scheme where two parents
OL,19,Fcould split 50 weeks of shared
OL,20,Fparental leave was introduced, but
OL,21,Fjust 5% of fathers take it.
